<h1>Gephex 0.0.4 Beta 2 Release Notes</h1>

<p>On November 4th 2003, the Gephex Project released Gephex 0.0.4beta2. This will be the last release before 0.0.4.</p>

<p>Gephex is a modular real-time video effect framework.
0.0.4beta2 provides lots of bug-fixes and some good new stuff. Our main
focus since 0.0.4alpha2 was to improve stability and usability.</p>

