<p>We fixed all severe open bugs and made the network code much more robust.
This allows to detach the user interface from the engine and to continue
the running effect.</p>

<p>Another benefit is its improved startup speed. Loading the plug-ins now only
takes a fraction of the time it did before.</p>

<p>As in every release, we have some new modules, most notably a
font module that uses the sdl_ttf library and more effecTV ports
(quarkTV for example).</p>

<p>To stabilize Gephex, we removed some nonfunctional parts,
such as the sequencer or the playlist. We did a code cleanup and removed
lots of old stuff.</p>

<p>For more details please see in the <a href="http://cvs.sourceforge.net/viewcvs.py/*checkout*/gephex/GePhex/NEWS?rev=1.13">Changelog</a>.</p>
